    <body>
        <section id="release-2.0.0" name="Release 2.0.0">
            <p>Features:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Set compatibility with Java 6+</li>
                <li>Set compatibility with Maven 3+</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Dependencies:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Upgraded <a href="http://lesscss-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/">LessCSS Compiler</a>
                    from <a href="http://lesscss-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/1.2.2/">1.2.2</a>
                    to <a href="http://lesscss-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/2.0.0/">2.0.0</a>
                    (<a href="https://github.com/gabrysbiz/lesscss-maven-plugin/issues/7">#7</a>)
                </li>
                <li>
                    Removed <a href="http://lesscss-extended-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/">Extended LessCSS Compiler</a>
                    (<a href="https://github.com/gabrysbiz/lesscss-maven-plugin/issues/7">#7</a>)
                </li>
                <li>
                    Upgraded <a href="http://maven-plugin-utils.projects.gabrys.biz/">Maven Plugin Utils</a>
                    from <a href="http://maven-plugin-utils.projects.gabrys.biz/1.4.0/">1.4.0</a>
                    to <a href="http://maven-plugin-utils.projects.gabrys.biz/2.0.0/">2.0.0</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="release-1.2.1" name="Release 1.2.1">
            <p>Dependencies:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Use <a href="http://lesscss-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/1.2.2/">LessCSS Compiler 1.2.2</a>
                    (fixed support for <code>data-uri</code> function - only for <code>local</code> compiler type)
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="release-1.2.0" name="Release 1.2.0">
            <p>Dependencies:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Upgraded <a href="http://lesscss-extended-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/">Extended LessCSS Compiler</a>
                    from <a href="http://lesscss-extended-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/2.0/">2.0</a>
                    to <a href="http://lesscss-extended-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/2.1.0/">2.1.0</a>
                    (support for <code>classpath://</code> protocol)
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="http://lesscss-maven-plugin.projects.gabrys.biz/1.2.0/">See documentation</a></p>
        </section>
        <section id="release-1.1" name="Release 1.1">
            <p>Dependencies:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Upgraded <a href="http://lesscss-extended-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/">Extended LessCSS Compiler</a>
                    from <a href="http://lesscss-extended-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/1.0/">1.0</a>
                    to <a href="http://lesscss-extended-compiler.projects.gabrys.biz/2.0/">2.0</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="http://lesscss-maven-plugin.projects.gabrys.biz/1.1/">See documentation</a></p>
        </section>
        <section id="release-1.0" name="Release 1.0">
            <p>Initial release.</p>
            <p><a href="http://lesscss-maven-plugin.projects.gabrys.biz/1.0/">See documentation</a></p>
        </section>
    </body>
